Perhaps they will cost 100k. They will not be something that the average lv51 or lv55 player will be able to buy for a few Kpp.<br>
They will not be sold very often. Players that have them will keep them or they have friends that need them.<br>
<br>
It looks like these items are not ment to be common among lv51-lv60 players.<br>
And that they are not ment to balance these players.<br>
