<br>
You can either be high enough level/in a strong guild/have lots of friends and get yourself a permanent focus item with good/decent stats, or you can kill brownie guards for 15 minutes each night and ask a mage to summon you an item.  You both get the same focus, and the same damage increase/etc. <p><br>
